header.gameNote: WEST COAST CONFERENCE MEN'S TOURNAMENT - SEMIFINAL

videos.description: Gonzaga's Nigel Williams-Goss with the great pass to Johnathan Williams who spins to make the layup.
videos.headline: Williams-Goss and Williams connect for layup

videos.description: Gonzaga's Killian Tillie puts in the hook shot for the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: Tillie hits the hook shot for Gonzaga

videos.description: Santa Clara's Jared Brownridge drains the 3-pointer as time expires in the first half.
videos.headline: Santa Clara hits 1st half buzzer-beater

videos.description: Gonzaga head coach Mark Few addresses the lack of defense on 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Few talks about giving up 3-pointers to Santa Clara

videos.description: Gonzaga's Jordan Matthews pump fakes to draw the defender than drives to the basket for the layup.
videos.headline: Matthews uses the pump fake to get the basket

videos.description: Santa Clara's Nate Kratch throws down the vicious two-handed slam for the Broncos to finish off a 10-0 run.
videos.headline: Santa Clara punctuates 10-0 run with dunk

videos.description: Gonzaga's Przemek Karnowski swats away Santa Clara's Jared Brownride's layup attempt.
videos.headline: Karnowski with the denial

videos.description: Gonzaga's Zach Collins hits the dagger 3-pointer to help the Bulldogs advance to the WCC final.
videos.headline: Collins seals it for Gonzaga with 3-pointer

videos.description: Gonzaga's Nigel Williams-Goss talks about the potential rematch against BYU in the WCC final.
videos.headline: Williams-Goss talks about looking for revenge against BYU
